item.title: Homage to Don Knotts
item.description: I want to take this opportunity to pay some homage to a great man that I had the pleasure of watching on TV at great lengths, thanks to my dad. Don Knotts, also know as Baney Fife from the Andy Griffith show. Rest In Peace: I found out from the Washington Post at this article: http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/02/25/AR2006022501535.html
